OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will see sunny
OL,6,Fspells interspersed with the odd
OL,7,Fshower. Cloud will increase over
OL,8,FOrkney in the afternoon with showers
OL,9,Fbecoming scattered here. Shetland will
OL,10,Fstay mostly dry and sunny through the
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe showers over Orkney will
OL,14,Fclear during the evening. This will
OL,15,Fleave the Isles mostly dry with clear
OL,16,Fspells through the night.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FThe day will stay dry with
OL,19,Fsunny spells, the best of these over
OL,20,FOrkney. A moderate southeast wind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
