OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Fband of rain will push north through
OL,7,FWednesday with scattered showers
OL,8,Ffollowing during Thursday. These
OL,9,Fshowers clear Thursday night to leave
OL,10,FFriday dry but cloudy.
